    AtlasNode { kind: "C", id: "hive_input_typing_slow_2026_05_02t02_25_axis_a_name_0", raw: "@C hive_input_typing_slow_2026_05_02t02_25_axis_a_name_0 = extension-count :: omega_cycle_hive-input-typing-slow-2026-05-02t02-25 [7]\n  => name of axis axis_a\n  => name of axis axis_a", source_file: "atlas.n6", source_line: 44882 },
    AtlasNode { kind: "C", id: "hive_input_typing_slow_2026_05_02t02_25_axis_a_summary_1", raw: "@C hive_input_typing_slow_2026_05_02t02_25_axis_a_summary_1 = Hypothesis: per-keystroke handler dispatch fan-out scales linearly with active extension count; each extension adds a synchronous middleware hop on the input path, dominating latency once N>~6. :: omega_cycle_hive-input-typing-slow-2026-05-02t02-25 [7]\n  => summary of axis axis_a\n  => summary of axis axis_a", source_file: "atlas.n6", source_line: 44886 },
